works.description: Dear Google, when you do a regular search and image search with ""chopper bobber ring" you will find that someone is using my images. I have filed prior reports before so if needed please look back to confirm that i am in fact a legit party here and these are my images. Just as before I would like to request the URLs below be removed from regular and image search. Please email again if needed and thank you for you help in the matter.
